\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sl231
\cf0 We  live in an age in which headlines can be taken directly from mainstream  newspapers, processed ever so slightly, then directly presented as  satire. This is making satirists jobs so much easier! Isn\'92t there an app  for that?]]></content:encoded> \
