\cf0 <content:encoded><![CDATA[After,  what seems like a direct channeling of distant memories of grade 11  biology combined with a recent visit to a reconstructed Iroquois [or  more correctly, <em>Haudenosaunee</em>:  People of the Longhouse] village, I had this thought: don\'92t the plans  of a <a href="http://www.nysm.nysed.gov/IroquoisVillage/" target="_blank">Iroquois village</a> with its longhouses and surrounding palisade look remarkably similar to  that of a biological cell? \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl233\sa230
